eNCA speaks to Musa Gumede from eThekwini Municipality for more details. #eNCA #DStv403  KWAZULU-NATAL - The government is on high alert and has activated emergency response systems amid heavy rains in KwaZulu-Natal. Officials are urging those who live in low lying areas to move to safer places. eNCA speaks to Musa Gumede from eThekwini Municipality for more details in the video above